	   <tr><td colspan=2>Woven spider silks are not the same as spider silks, nor can one be made into another as far as I know.&nbsp;&nbsp;The woven spider silks are required for at least the Kelethin druid newbie armor quest, probably other newbie quests as well.  I am not aware of any use for them beyond those quests (in particular, no tailoring recipes), and I would suspect that's their only purpose.  Regular spider silks are what you want for tailoring.<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
